---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="ICN Use Cases" description="Infrastructure for timebanks, mutual credit systems, and cooperative coordination">
  <section class="pt-32 pb-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="bg-accent-primary/20 text-accent-primary border border-accent-primary/30 text-sm font-bold px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-4 inline-block">
          USE CASES
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">What ICN Enables</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-light-slate max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          ICN provides infrastructure for timebanks, mutual credit systems, and cooperative
          coordination. Here's what communities can build with it.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-8">
        <!-- Timebanks -->
        <div class="bg-midnight-navy/50 p-8 rounded-lg border border-accent-primary/20">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-primary/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-2xl">‚è∞</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent-primary">Timebanks</h2>
              <p class="text-slate-gray">Hour-for-hour exchange systems</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-light-slate mb-6">
            ICN's mutual credit ledger is designed for timebanking. Members log hours given
            and received, with double-entry accounting ensuring the books always balance.
          </p>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
            <ul class="text-light-slate space-y-2">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Hour logging with categories</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Member balance tracking</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Activity history and charts</li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="text-light-slate space-y-2">
              <li>‚Ä¢ CSV export for treasurers</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Mobile-friendly interface</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Trust-based member verification</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Mutual Credit -->
        <div class="bg-midnight-navy/50 p-8 rounded-lg border border-accent-blue/20">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-blue/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-2xl">üí±</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent-blue">Mutual Credit Systems</h2>
              <p class="text-slate-gray">Community currencies without external money</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-light-slate mb-6">
            Create community currencies backed by mutual trust rather than external assets.
            Members can go into negative balance (credit) and positive balance (debit),
            with the network always summing to zero.
          </p>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
            <ul class="text-light-slate space-y-2">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Dynamic credit limits</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Trust-based line increases</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Dispute resolution mechanisms</li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="text-light-slate space-y-2">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Real-time balance tracking</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Transaction transparency</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Merkle-DAG anchoring</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Worker Cooperatives -->
        <div class="bg-midnight-navy/50 p-8 rounded-lg border border-accent-purple/20">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-purple/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-2xl">üè≠</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent-purple">Worker Cooperatives</h2>
              <p class="text-slate-gray">Democratic workplace coordination</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-light-slate mb-6">
            Worker cooperatives can use ICN for member management, democratic decision-making,
            and resource allocation. The governance system supports one-member-one-vote
            and configurable quorum rules.
          </p>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
            <ul class="text-light-slate space-y-2">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Member onboarding with DIDs</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Proposal and voting system</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Transparent decision records</li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="text-light-slate space-y-2">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Configurable governance rules</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Trust-based role assignment</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Federation with other coops</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Community Governance -->
        <div class="bg-midnight-navy/50 p-8 rounded-lg border border-accent-glow/20">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-glow/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-2xl">üèõÔ∏è</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent-glow">Community Governance</h2>
              <p class="text-slate-gray">Participatory decision-making</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-light-slate mb-6">
            Neighborhood associations, housing cooperatives, and community groups can use
            ICN for participatory governance. Residents verify identity, make proposals,
            and vote on community decisions.
          </p>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
            <ul class="text-light-slate space-y-2">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Resident verification</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Domain-scoped proposals</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Time-bounded voting</li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="text-light-slate space-y-2">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Automatic execution on approval</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Voting history records</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Mobile participation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Federation -->
        <div class="bg-midnight-navy/50 p-8 rounded-lg border border-slate-600">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-slate-600/50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-2xl">üåê</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Federation</h2>
              <p class="text-slate-gray">Networks of cooperatives</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-light-slate mb-6">
            Multiple cooperatives can federate to share resources, coordinate on larger
            projects, and maintain local autonomy while participating in a larger network.
            Each cooperative runs their own node(s) and controls their own governance.
          </p>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
            <ul class="text-light-slate space-y-2">
              <li>‚Ä¢ Cross-coop resource sharing</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Federation-level governance</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Maintained local autonomy</li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="text-light-slate space-y-2">
              <li>‚Ä¢ QUIC/TLS secure networking</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Trust-gated communication</li>
              <li>‚Ä¢ Gossip protocol propagation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA -->
        <div class="bg-accent-glow/10 p-8 rounded-lg border border-accent-glow/30 text-center">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent-glow mb-4">Ready to Try ICN?</h2>
          <p class="text-light-slate mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            ICN is PILOT-READY with 20 development phases complete. Clone the repo
            and start exploring, or contact us about pilot deployments.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="/get-started"
               class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 bg-accent-glow text-midnight-navy font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-accent-glow/90 transition-colors">
              Get Started
            </a>
            <a href="https://github.com/InterCooperative-Network/icn"
               target="_blank"
               class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 bg-transparent border-2 border-accent-glow text-accent-glow font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-accent-glow hover:text-midnight-navy transition-colors">
              View Source
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
